    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you\u2019ve completed"
            }
          ],
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "THE FALL OF SPIRE:"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You wake up, jolted out of sleep by visions of reclaimers\noverrunning Spire, spilling into the arcology, their strange voices\ncrowing in victory. You take a deep breath, splash water on your\nface, and remind yourself that the danger has passed. All the\nsame, you feel the need to be a bit more alert than usual today."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Each Ranger gains one energy in an aspect of their choice for the\nfirst round."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you haven\u2019t:"
            }
          ],
          "color": "red"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You're jolted out of sleep by a hand on your shoulder. It's Kal\nIver. His cloak is torn, and he's covered in either dirt or soot."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\"Wake up,\" he says. \"I thought you might be dead, but here you\nare, sleeping peacefully while the village of Spire was destroyed\nand thousands of people were displaced. We could have used\nyour help, you know. I hope whatever you were busy doing was\nof equal importance.\""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "He looks with dismay at a rend in his cloak. \"You must travel to\nLone Tree Station. Elder Thrush wants all Rangers to check in as\nsoon as they are able.\" With that, Kal departs."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Complete the"
        },
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "SPIRE UNDER ATTACK"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "mission, and gain"
        },
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "JOURNEY (LONE TREE STATION)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". Record"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "SPIRE FALLEN"
            }
          ],
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "and"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "MISSED IT"
            }
          ],
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "on the campaign tracker."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
